Class MultiPointXY

java.lang.Object
  gov.nasa.ial.mde.math.MultiPointXY

public class MultiPointXY
extends Object

A generalization of the PointXY class that includes the idea of multiple (or no) y values corresponding to a given x.

Since:
1.0
Version:
1.0
Author:
Dr. Robert Shelton
